州旗的顏色和圖案具有文化、政治和地域的含義，作為底圖的[[藍船旗|藍船旗]]象徵澳洲曾是[[大不列顛及愛爾蘭聯合王國|英國]]殖民地的歷史，而澳洲其他5個[[澳洲行政區劃|聯邦州]]均以該旗幟為底，唯一的區別在於各州旗上不同的圖案紋章<ref name=factsheet/><ref name="DK">{{cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/complete-flags-of-the-world-5th-edition-dk-2009/page/222/mode/2up|title=Complete Flags of the World|publisher=Penguin|year=2009|last=Kindersley Ltd.|first=Dorling|page=223|isbn=9780756654863|language=en}}</ref>；黑天鵝則代表西澳洲本身<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6OG1CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA258|title=D.H. Lawrence's Australia: Anxiety at the Edge of Empire|publisher=Routledge|date=2016-03-09|last=Game|first=David|page=258|isbn=9781317155058|language=en|access-date=2020-10-09|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209031044/https://books.google.com/books?id=6OG1CwAAQBAJ&pg=PA258|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Giblett">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hcBX50DwRTkC&pg=PA69|title=Black Swan Lake: Life of a Wetland|publisher=Intellect Books|year=2013|last=Giblett|first=Rodney James|page=69|isbn=9781841507040|access-date=2020-09-19|archivedate=2020-09-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927214909/https://books.google.com/books?id=hcBX50DwRTkC&pg=PA69|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>，該鳥類是西澳州的[[原生物種|原生物種]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Ask an expert: Do black and white swans interbreed?|url=https://ww2.rspb.org.uk/birds-and-wildlife/bird-and-wildlife-guides/ask-an-expert/previous/swaninterbreeding.aspx|accessdate=2020-09-05|date=2010-01-04|last=Scott|first=Lloyd|publisher=Royal Society for the Protection of Birds|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190709175129/https://ww2.rspb.org.uk/birds-and-wildlife/bird-and-wildlife-guides/ask-an-expert/previous/swaninterbreeding.aspx|archivedate=2019-07-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Rare black swan spotted 9,000 miles from home on River Severn|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/black-swan-worcester-river-severn-uk-wild-population-rare-birds-a8490041.html|first=Tom|last=Barnes|date=2018-08-13|accessdate=2020-09-05|newspaper=The Independent|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418113807/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/black-swan-worcester-river-severn-uk-wild-population-rare-birds-a8490041.html|archivedate=2020-04-18|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其名也成為天鵝河殖民地（今西澳州的前身）命名的依據<ref name=EB/>，黑天鵝於1973年7月25日被確立為該州的[[澳大利亚州鸟列表|州鳥]]<ref name=factsheet/>，根據作者羅德尼·詹姆斯·吉布利特（Rodney James Giblett）的說法「黑天鵝已成為澳洲反對英國[[帝國主義|帝國主義]]的[[民族主義|民族主義]]代表」。<ref name=Giblett/>

== 禮儀 ==
[[File:Coat_of_Arms_of_Australia.svg|200px]]，中央的盾牌可見黑天鵝圖案位於其第二行的中間處]]
與州旗有關的{{tsl|en|Flag protocol|旗幟禮儀}}由西澳大利亚州州长與內閣部（Department of the Premier and Cabinet）負責。<ref name="protocol">{{cite web|title=Premier and Cabinet protocol and State events – flags|url=https://www.wa.gov.au/organisation/department-of-the-premier-and-cabinet/premier-and-cabinet-protocol-and-state-events-flags|accessdate=2020-09-05|date=2019-09-19|work=Department of the Premier and Cabinet|publisher=Government of Western Australia|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200905191420/https://www.wa.gov.au/organisation/department-of-the-premier-and-cabinet/premier-and-cabinet-protocol-and-state-events-flags|archivedate=2020-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>當西澳州州旗與[[澳洲國旗|澳洲國旗]]及其他州旗、領地旗同時懸掛時，西澳洲旗在[[啄序|等級順序]]中位列第六（國旗之後，二至五依序為[[新南威爾斯州旗|新南威爾斯州旗]]、[[維多利亞州旗|維多利亞州旗]]、[[昆士蘭州旗|昆士蘭州旗]]和[[南澳州州旗|南澳州州旗]]）<ref>{{cite book|title=Australian Flags booklet: part two|url=https://www.pmc.gov.au/sites/default/files/publications/australian-flags-excerpt.pdf|edition=3|page=25|date=2006-07-20|accessdate=2020-09-05|work=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet|publisher=Government of Australia|isbn=0642471347|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724221856/https://www.pmc.gov.au/sites/default/files/publications/australian-flags-excerpt.pdf|archivedate=2020-07-24|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這也顯示該州的黑天鵝圖案在[[澳洲國徽|澳洲國徽]]盾牌上的位置，其位列國徽第二行的中間處（由左而右、上而下第五位）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Commonwealth Coat of Arms|url=https://www.pmc.gov.au/government/commonwealth-coat-arms|accessdate=2020-09-06|work=Department of the Prime Minister and Cabinet|publisher=Government of Australia|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200730090610/https://www.pmc.gov.au/government/commonwealth-coat-arms|archivedate=2020-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據指引規定，州旗不得與地面接觸，也不得與其他旗幟懸掛於同一旗桿。除非需在夜間將旗幟照亮，否則州旗應在黎明前升起，且須在黃昏前降下，而唯一的例外是[[降半旗|降半旗]]時，不論是否在夜間亮起均不得整夜懸掛。同時不得以倒掛的方式懸掛州旗，即使其目的是發出{{tsl|en|Distress signal|求救信號}}。<ref name=protocol/>

